*glitter-1.0-r1 (17 Jan 2005)

  17 Jan 2005; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> +metadata.xml,
  +files/glitter-1.0-gary-perl58.patch, +glitter-1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Moved from net-news/glitter to net-nntp/glitter.

  14 Jul 2004; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> glitter-1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Added alternative SRC_URI as the official one seems to be dead.

  05 Jul 2004; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> glitter-1.0-r1.ebuild,
  -glitter-1.0.ebuild:
  Removed older ebuild. Updated dependencies and ebuild cleanup.

  19 Jun 2004; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> +metadata.xml:
  Added metadata.xml

  07 Jun 2003; <rac@gentoo.org> glitter-1.0-r1.ebuild, glitter-1.0.ebuild:
  Add IUSE

*glitter-1.0-r1 (01 Jun 2003)

  01 Jun 2003; <rac@gentoo.org> glitter-1.0-r1.ebuild, glitter-1.0.ebuild,
  files/glitter-1.0-gary-perl58.patch:
